âœ… Conclusion

This project showcases how AI and NLP techniques can convert raw, unstructured consumer data into meaningful and actionable insights. By integrating data cleaning, sentiment analysis, and topic modeling, the system empowers organizations to understand customer behavior, anticipate market trends, and respond proactively to business challenges.
